# Section 2: Wedding Celebrations (3-Day Timeline)

The heart of the invitation. A 3-day celebration timeline with all events organized by date. Each event is a self-contained royal scroll card with venue, address, and map link built in.

---

## Purpose

Guests see what's happening, where, and how to get there — all in one place. Each day is a "chapter" with tab navigation. No separate venue section needed.

