## Event Card Design (Royal Scroll / Farmaan Style)

Each card looks like a royal farmaan (decree) — ornate scroll edges, wax seal, fully self-contained with venue + directions.

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Card Background | `#111E36` with 1px `#C9A96E` border at 20% opacity |
| Border Radius | 16px |
| Shadow | `0 4px 20px rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.08)` |
| Padding | 24px mobile, 32px desktop |
| Scroll Top Edge | Curved SVG ornament resembling rolled parchment. `#C9A96E` at 12% opacity. Gentle curves (5-8px displacement), not dramatic |
| Scroll Bottom Edge | Mirror of top ornament — creates farmaan silhouette |
| Wax Seal Motif | 16px circular gold seal at top-center. SVG with mandala/lotus pattern. `#C9A96E` |
| Implementation | CSS `::before`/`::after` pseudo-elements with SVG background, OR `border-image` with SVG source |

### Card Content Layout

| Element | Font / Style | Color |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Event Name | Cormorant Garamond 600, 20px | `#C9A96E` gold |
| Hindi Name | Mukta Vaani 400, 14px | `#8A8578` muted |
| Date & Time | Lora 400, 14px | `#D4CFC5` cream |
| Dress Code | Small tag/badge — Inter 500, 11px, gold 1px border, 4px padding, 6px radius | `#D4CFC5` text, `#C9A96E` border |
| Separator | 1px line, `#C9A96E` at 10% opacity | — |
| Venue Name | Cormorant Garamond 500, 16px | `#D4CFC5` cream |
| Full Address | Lora 400, 13px | `#8A8578` muted |
| Map Button | Gold outlined pill — Inter 500, 13px, 1px `#C9A96E` border, 8px/16px padding, 20px radius | `#D4CFC5` text, arrow `#C9A96E` |

### Map Button Behavior

- Text: "📍 Open in Maps →"
- Opens Google Maps link in new tab
- Hover: arrow animates right 4px, border brightens to `#D4B87A`
- Tap (mobile): immediate open, gold ripple feedback

### Card Animation

- On day tab switch: cards stagger in (0.15s delay between each card)
- On first load: cards fade in + slide up 20px, staggered
- Card hover (desktop): gold border brightens, shadow increases, wax seal gets subtle golden glow

