## Section 2 Specs

- Background: `#0A1628` with subtle gradient
- This section allows INTERNAL scrolling (day tabs sticky at top, cards scroll vertically) — unlike other sections which are fixed 100vh
- Min height: 100vh, can extend based on number of cards
- Jaali texture: Faint paisley borders at left and right edges, 5% opacity
- Navigation Button: "Next: Gallery →" — always visible at bottom of section (fixed position within section, above fold)
- Transition In: Fade + gold particle sweep from left to right (0.8s, ease-in-out)
- Transition Out: Soft cross-fade (0.6s) to Gallery